ExportItemConfig.Query:
SELECT * FROM gs_sale_tag WHERE merchant_id={merchant_id}
AND ({enabled}<0 OR enabled={enabled}) AND ( tag_name Like '%{keyword}%'
  OR tag_code LIKE '%{keyword}%') limit {page_start},{page_size}

ExportItemConfig.Total:
SELECT COUNT(0) FROM gs_sale_tag WHERE merchant_id={merchant_id}
AND ({enabled}<0 OR enabled={enabled}) AND ( tag_name Like '%{keyword}%'
  OR tag_code LIKE '%{keyword}%')
